Time Limit
    - Arcade is only open between certain hours
    - Each user can only be logged in for 1 hour per day

Token Restrictions
    - Each game should cost some number of tokens to play
    - Restrict the amount of tokens that any given game awards

Gift Shop
    - Spend your tokens on:
        - emojis that display with your username (e.g., in the leaderboard)
        - in-game abilities (e.g., re-spin in slots) that you burn as you use them
        - username enhancements (e.g., "<username> The Great!")
